extendedInfo.description: Welcome to College Freshmen!College 101: Freshmen Tips include a TON of valuable information that every new and current college freshmen should know! Includes a ton of features! FREE!************************************INFORMATION INCLUDES:************************************- What to do before college starts?- What to bring to college?- What NOT to bring to college?- Financial tips - learn them!- The Freshmen dictionary!- How to be popular?- The top 10 things you need to know!- What classes should you take?- Homework Disasters... and how to avoid.- Buying / Renting Textbooks!- How to stay and eat healthy in college.- The dreaded freshmen 15!- 10 tips for good grades.- College application advice & tipsand MORE!************************************APP FEATURES INCLUDES:************************************- Sleek, easy, and beautiful design!- iPhone and iPad compatibility!- Socialize SDK! (comments, likes, shares)- Rate this app!- Notepad! (make notes and save them in the app!)- Calculator (simple calculator for fast math!)- Search! (do in app content searches!)- QUIZ! (are you ready for college, freshmen?)- Blogs & Sites (quick links to resourceful websites!)- Share via texting and email features!and MORE!Thanks for downloading, and best of luck freshmen!* This was a joint application made possible by Campus Orb - visit them at CampusOrb.com! (includes support)Sam & David
